origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "Insurance.service_comparison",
        "description": "比较不同保险服务的优劣，帮助用户选择最适合的保险产品。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison",
                "description": "返回不同保险服务的比较结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.case_study",
        "description": "提供具体的保险案例研究，帮助用户理解保险产品的实际应用。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "case_study",
                "description": "返回具体的保险案例研究内容。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.premium_calculator",
        "description": "根据用户输入的参数计算保险费用，帮助用户预估保险成本。",
        "required_parameters": ["age", "coverage_amount"],
        "optional_parameters": ["additional_coverage"],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "premium",
                "description": "返回计算出的保险费用。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.claim_process",
        "description": "提供保险理赔流程的详细说明，帮助用户了解如何进行理赔。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "process_steps",
                "description": "返回保险理赔的详细步骤。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.tax_optimization_strategy",
        "description": "提供税务优化策略，帮助用户在购买保险时最大化税务优惠。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "description",
                "description": "返回税务优化策略的详细描述。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.risk_assessment",
        "description": "根据用户的风险偏好和财务状况，评估其保险需求。",
        "required_parameters": ["risk_tolerance", "income"],
        "optional_parameters": ["family_size"],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "assessment_result",
                "description": "返回风险评估的结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.recommendation",
        "description": "根据用户的需求和风险评估，推荐最适合的保险产品。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "recommendation",
                "description": "返回推荐的保险产品信息。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
